# Build artifacts only. The sqltgen output directories (src/db, gen,
# src/main/java/com/example/db, etc.) are NOT ignored — they are committed
# so that snapshot-diff can detect codegen drift before running runtime
# tests (see docs/E2E_RUNTIME_STATUS.md for the snapshot-as-gate workflow).

# Rust
**/target/
**/Cargo.lock.bak

# Java / Kotlin (Maven)
**/target/
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings/

# Eclipse / IntelliJ scratch files
**/.idea/
**/*.iml

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/*.pyc

# Node
**/node_modules/

# Go
**/vendor/
